Package WizardTD.Tile

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Grass
    The Grass class extends the Tile class and is suitable for tower placement but not for enemy movement.
    IceTower
    The IceTower class represents an ice-themed tower in the game, which can slow and attack enemies within its range.
    PathTile
    The PathTile class extends the Tile class and is suitable for enemy movement but not for tower placement.
    Shrub
    The Shrub class extends the Tile class and represents a decorative tile that is neither suitable for tower placement nor enemy movement.
    SpawnTile
    The SpawnTile class extends the PathTile class and represents a tile used as the starting point for enemy spawns.
    Tile
    The Tile class represents a tile in the GameMap, which can be used for towers to be placed on or enemies to walk on.
    Tower
    The Tower class represents a tower in the game, which can attack enemies within its range.
    WizardHome
    The WizardHome class extends the Tile class and is the endpoint for all enemy paths in the game.
